html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    title Location Revenue Report
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='./css/main.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', type='text/css', href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css')
    script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.4.min.js')
    script(src='./js/main.js')
  body
    header.container-fluid
      .row
        .col-xs-4
          img.img-responsive(src='./img/alsco-logo.png')
        .col-xs-8
          | Location Revenue Per Pound Runner
    .main-panel.container-fluid
      #instructions.container-fluid
        h3 Instructions
        p
          | To use this web application, follow the following steps:
          ol
            li
              | Run the Revenue Per Pound Report from Alsco CRS
              ol
                li Go the Alsco CRS and log in
                li Click on the 'Financial' category
                li Click on Revenue Per Pound Report
                li Enter the desired month, region, and plant
                li Set the output type to xls
                li Click the Run report button
                li
                  | When the report is finished, click 'View Report' and download the 'Location Summary' file
                li Choose that report as the first file on this site
            li
              | Run the National Account Listing report from Abel.
              ol
                li Login to the branch Abel system
                li
                  | Run and save the report located under Processing > Reports > On Demand Reports > National Account Listing
                li Open the csv file that was generated
                li Save the file as an xlsx or xls file using Excel
                li Choose that report as the second file on this site
            li Click Submit and wait for the results to download
        h3 Additional Info
        p
          | You can also download an application version of this report by following 
          a(href='./download') this
          |  link.
        p
          | Note: You will need java 8 update 101 to run the application version. You can download the latest version of java by following 
          a(href='https://www.java.com/en/download/windows-64bit.jsp', target='_blank') this
          |  link.
      form#report-form(action='/run', method='POST', enctype='multipart/form-data')
        .form-group
          label(for='rev-report') Revenue Report From CRS
          input#rev-report.form-control(type='file', name='reqFiles', accept='application/vnd.ms-excel,application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet', required='')
        .form-group
          label(for='nat-report') National Acct Listing from Abel
          input#nat-report.form-control(type='file', name='reqFiles', accept='application/vnd.ms-excel,application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet', required='')
        .form-group
          input#submit-button.form-control.btn.btn-default(type='submit')
    footer
